        <item>
            <title>1.4.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 21:54:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/martinfekete10/Tuneful/releases</link>
            <sparkle:version>1.4.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.4.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>Scrolling menu bar text</h1>
<ul>
<li>Menu bar text is now scrolling if it does not fit the max width</li>
<li>New option to hide menu bar text when nothing is currently playing</li>
<li>New keyboard shortcut to quickly switch between Spotify and Apple Music</li>
<li>Ability to switch between Spotify and Apple Music from new menu bar submenu</li>
<li>Fixed an issue when incremental volume increase would break the UI on max volume</li>
<li>Fixed an issue when progress bar would not update until the mini player window is displayed for the first time</li>
<li>Minor settings improvements</li>
<li>Minor mini player improvements</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
